name: Backflip Master - Parkour Game
description:
Backflip Master - a dynamic game with unique gameplay, on the basis of physics character. A full ragdoll system gives you madness in the game. Come locations performing extreme jumps and stunts. The Parkour system helps you unlock your tricks skills.
Backflip master have a lot of tricks - pike, scissors, candle, flip, reverse bent...
Dive into the mad world of extreme jumps and stunts!
